{"id": "1483906445714915468", "channel_id": "1483901221344379060", "type": 0, "author_id": "706262934485073951", "author_name": "bagels5899", "author_bot": false, "content": "for healers Remove Xu and move Lily and Gdoll up one tier, slot Celeste at #5. Honestly high con is a pretty good way of staying alive especially in Caro, but that isn’t something only Xu can do if that makes sense, Celeste is also pretty good\n\nCastor and Faint swap places, Faint is good but can only prolongue your life for so long whereas you can pretty reasonably stall with Castor for a very long time so long as the enemy doesn’t ramp out of control while also enabling burst turns with his corrosion/draw/plume arith\n\nI think shuffle Horla all the way to the bottom, 0 cost aliemus is nice but its not a ton… and joybotting has its own issues\n\nIdk a ton about all the relics but I think dagger even being on this list is already kinda sketch since its only for counter, idk just how good it is to call something “some of the best” when it is only good on one meh setup. Would also argue moving pipe to #4, cup and insignia are just that good", "timestamp": "2026-03-18T19:14:26.307000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-18T19:15:09.487000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
